title: Spectacular double overhead kick in Thai League football match – video
text:
It's rare enough to see an overhead kick goal in a game, but one match in the Thai League produced a double one as two players both jumped into the air. The pair, who play for Nakhon Ratchasima FC, leapt at the same time and both attempted an overhead kick. Defensive midfielder Kitsada Hemvipat and Brazilian Leandro Assumpcao were the two players involved, although Kitsada claimed the goal. However, it came too late in the game as Buriram United ran out 3-2 victors

Video courtesy of Thai League
